#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Youkai Enemies"
msgstr "妖怪敌人"

#. ~ Description for Youkai Enemies
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds some monsters based off Japanese folklore."
msgstr "添加了一些基于日本民间传说的怪物。"

#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgid "The %1$s directs some dust into your eyes!"
msgstr "%1$s 将一些灰尘吹进了你的眼睛！"

#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgid "The %1$s directs dust into <npcname>'s eyes!"
msgstr "%1$s 将灰尘吹进了 <npcname> 的眼睛！"

#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgid ""
"The %1$s tries to direct dust into your eyes, but it just flows around your "
"face!"
msgstr "%1$s 试图将灰尘吹进你的眼睛，但灰尘只是从你脸旁飘过！"

#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgid ""
"The %1$s tries to direct dust into <npcname>'s eyes, but it just flows "
"around their face!"
msgstr "%1$s 试图将灰尘吹进 <npcname> 的眼睛，但灰尘只是从他们脸旁飘过！"

#: .\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "field"
msgstr "田野"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "tengu thug"
msgid_plural "tengu thugs"
msgstr[0] "天狗暴徒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tengu thug'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"A tall person with a red face and a long nose, covered in black feathers "
"with wings on its back, wearing a kimono with a mischievous look in the eye."
"  With a quick glance you also spot its sharp claws, and a wooden club by "
"its belt."
msgstr "一个高个子，红脸长鼻，浑身覆盖着黑色羽毛，背生双翼，身穿和服，眼中闪烁着顽皮的光芒。你快速一瞥，还看到了它锋利的爪子，以及腰间别着的木棍。"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "tengu monk"
msgid_plural "tengu monks"
msgstr[0] "天狗僧侣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tengu monk'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"A tall person with a red face and a long nose, with most of its head however"
" covered up by rags.  From under its kimono you can spot pieces of Japanese "
"armor.  It often meditates and is probably best left to itself.  As for "
"weapons, it's holding a naginata, a dangerous polearm."
msgstr ""
"一个高个子，红脸长鼻，但头部大部分被破布遮盖。从它的和服下，你可以看到日本盔甲的碎片。它经常冥想，最好别去打扰它。至于武器，它手持一把薙刀，一种危险的长柄武器。"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "cat"
msgid_plural "cats"
msgstr[0] "猫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cat'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"A small domesticated predator gone feral in the absence of human "
"stewardship.  Harried by the elements and the rigors of survival, it waggles"
" its two tails...  Wait, nevermind, that's probably not your ordinary cat."
msgstr "一只小型家养捕食者，在失去人类照料后变得狂野。饱受恶劣环境和生存艰辛的折磨，它摇晃着两条尾巴……等等，别在意，那可能不是普通的猫。"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "kappa"
msgid_plural "kappas"
msgstr[0] "河童"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'kappa'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"A small humanoid the size of child, with frog-like skin and turtle-like "
"carapace on it's back.  It carries water in a cavity in its skull, has a "
"sharp beak and is known to drag people under the water in order to eat them."
"  It would prefer cucumbers however."
msgstr ""
"一个孩童大小的小型人形生物，皮肤似蛙，背有龟壳般的甲壳。它的头骨凹陷处存有水，长着锋利的喙，以将人拖入水中吃掉而闻名。不过，它其实更喜欢黄瓜。"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "kappa engineer"
msgid_plural "kappa engineers"
msgstr[0] "河童工程师"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'kappa engineer'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"A small humanoid the size of child, with frog-like skin and turtle-like "
"carapace on it's back.  It carries water in a cavity in its skull and "
"strangely enough in this case a bunch of tools.  What would it need those "
"for?"
msgstr "一个孩童大小的小型人形生物，皮肤似蛙，背有龟壳般的甲壳。它的头骨凹陷处存有水，奇怪的是，这次还带着一堆工具。它要这些做什么？"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "mysterious robot"
msgid_plural "mysterious robots"
msgstr[0] "神秘机器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mysterious robot'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"On the outside this robot seems to be of a very old design, similar in look "
"to ancient Japanese automata.  Then you notice its giant size and the fact "
"that, among many unfamiliar symbols, it has a three-leafed nuclear hazard "
"sign."
msgstr ""
"从外表看，这个机器人似乎设计非常古老，外观类似于日本古代的自动人偶。然后你注意到它巨大的体型，以及一个事实：在许多陌生的符号中，它有一个三叶形的核辐射警告标志。"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "oni bandit"
msgid_plural "oni bandits"
msgstr[0] "鬼族强盗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'oni bandit'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"A huge, muscular person with blood red skin, glaring at you with rage, "
"wearing animal skins and wielding a giant log as a makeshift club.  Under "
"its singular horn stares at you a smaller, third eye, surrounded by unkempt "
"hair."
msgstr ""
"一个高大、肌肉发达的人，皮肤血红，愤怒地瞪着你，身穿兽皮，挥舞着一根巨大的原木作为临时棍棒。在它那根独角下，一只较小的第三只眼正盯着你，周围是蓬乱的头发。"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "kamaitachi"
msgid_plural "kamaitachis"
msgstr[0] "镰鼬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'kamaitachi'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"A small weasel-like creature, with four sickles instead of its four paws. It"
" flies on an unending gust of hot wind filled with dust and seems to be able"
" to control its direction."
msgstr "一只小型鼬鼠般的生物，四只爪子被四把镰刀取代。它乘着一股永不停歇、充满灰尘的热风飞行，似乎能够控制其方向。"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "okka"
msgid_plural "okkas"
msgstr[0] "御加"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'okka'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"A small bulbous creature with red, frog-like skin. It runs around on its two"
" tiny clawed feets, hiding from people's sight."
msgstr "一个红色、蛙皮般的小型球状生物。它用两只带爪的小脚跑来跑去，躲避人们的视线。"

#: .\youkai.json
msgid "kanazuchibo"
msgid_plural "kanazuchibos"
msgstr[0] "金槌坊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'kanazuchibo'}
#: .\youkai.json
msgid ""
"A  tiny humanoid with grey, wrinkly skin and long, uncombed silver hair. It "
"carries around absurdly large wooden hammer, given its size."
msgstr "一个灰色皮肤皱巴巴、银色长发未梳理的微小类人生物。考虑到它的体型，它扛着一把大得离谱的木锤。"

#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid "sake"
msgid_plural "sake"
msgstr[0] "清酒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sake', 'str_pl': 'sake'}
#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid ""
"A popular Japanese alcohol made by fermenting and filtering rice with the "
"use of yeast and special mold called \"koji\".  This one is crystal clear "
"and holding it makes you feel rather fancy."
msgstr "一种流行的日本酒，通过用酵母和称为“麴”的特殊霉菌发酵并过滤大米制成。这款酒清澈透明，拿着它让你感觉相当精致。"

#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid "koji & yeast starter"
msgid_plural "koji & yeast starters"
msgstr[0] "麴与酵母起子"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'koji & yeast starter'}.
#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid ""
"The koji seems to have overtaken the entire batch of rice, you form it into "
"a tiny \"cake\" for later use."
msgstr "麴似乎已经覆盖了整批大米，你将其塑成一个小“饼”以备后用。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'koji & yeast starter'}.
#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid "The koji still has plenty of room to grow..."
msgstr "麴仍有很大的生长空间……"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'koji & yeast starter'}
#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid ""
"Bunch of cooked table rice mixed with yeast and koji mold fragments, set a "
"side to grow moldy so it can make a passable sake base."
msgstr "一堆煮熟的米饭混合了酵母和麴霉碎片，放在一旁发霉，以便制成可用的清酒基料。"

#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid "koji covered rice"
msgid_plural "koji covered rice"
msgstr[0] "覆盖麴的米饭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'koji covered rice', 'str_pl': 'koji covered
#. rice'}
#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid ""
"Bunch of rice covered in a distinct mold, mixed in with yeast.  Useful for "
"making sake, but not really tasty on its own.  Smells vaguely of chestnuts."
msgstr "一堆覆盖着独特霉菌的米饭，混有酵母。可用于制作清酒，但本身并不美味。闻起来隐约有栗子味。"

#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid "sake base"
msgid_plural "sake bases"
msgstr[0] "清酒基料"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sake base'}
#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid ""
"A fine mix of water, koji covered rice and yeast, ready to be fermented into"
" sake once set in a fermenting vat."
msgstr "水、覆盖麴的米饭和酵母的精细混合物，一旦放入发酵桶中即可发酵成清酒。"

#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid "nigori sake"
msgid_plural "nigori sake"
msgstr[0] "浊酒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nigori sake', 'str_pl': 'nigori sake'}
#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid ""
"A Japanese alcohol made by fermenting rice with the use of yeast and special"
" mold called \"koji\".  It hasn't been pressed so it has a white, cloudy "
"texture because of rice base sendiments.  You can probaly filter it to make "
"it look more refined."
msgstr ""
"一种日本酒，通过用酵母和称为“麴”的特殊霉菌发酵大米制成。它未经压榨，因此由于米基沉淀物而呈现白色浑浊质地。你或许可以过滤它，使其看起来更精致。"

#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid "koji"
msgid_plural "koji"
msgstr[0] "曲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'koji', 'str_pl': 'koji'}
#: .\youkai_brewing.json
msgid ""
"A powdered mix of ground rice and fragments of Aspergillus oryzae fungus, "
"set aside for later use in making sake."
msgstr "磨碎的大米和米曲霉碎片的粉末混合物，留待以后制作清酒时使用。"

#: .\youkai_factions.json
msgid "youkai"
msgid_plural "youkais"
msgstr[0] "妖怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'youkai'}
#: .\youkai_factions.json
msgid "Youkai"
msgstr "妖怪"

#: .\youkai_factions.json
msgid "Order side youkai"
msgid_plural "Order side youkais"
msgstr[0] "秩序侧妖怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Order side youkai'}
#: .\youkai_factions.json
msgid "Order side"
msgstr "秩序侧"

#: .\youkai_factions.json
msgid "Chaos side youkai"
msgid_plural "Chaos side youkais"
msgstr[0] "混沌侧妖怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chaos side youkai'}
#: .\youkai_factions.json
msgid "Chaos side"
msgstr "混沌侧"

#: .\youkai_items.json
msgid "broken mysterious robot"
msgid_plural "broken mysterious robots"
msgstr[0] "损坏的神秘机器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken mysterious robot'}
#: .\youkai_items.json
msgid ""
"A gigantic heap of weird metal parts, hoses, pipes and plutonium.  It makes "
"no sense as far as your electrical knowledge is concerned, but it can always"
" be gutted for parts."
msgstr "一堆巨大的怪异金属零件、软管、管道和钚。就你的电气知识而言，这毫无意义，但它总可以被拆解成零件。"

#: .\youkai_items.json
msgid "pair of nekomata tails"
msgid_plural "pairs of nekomata tails"
msgstr[0] "一对猫又尾巴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of nekomata tails', 'str_pl': 'pairs of
#. nekomata tails'}
#: .\youkai_items.json
msgid ""
"A pair of feline tails, grown together in a otherworldly but charming "
"manner.  Eating them could potentially mutate you into a more purr-fect "
"form."
msgstr "一对猫科动物的尾巴，以超凡脱俗但迷人的方式长在一起。食用它们可能会让你变异成更完美的形态。"

#: .\youkai_items.json
msgid "wooden kine"
msgid_plural "wooden kines"
msgstr[0] "木杵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wooden kine'}
#: .\youkai_items.json
msgid ""
"A large wooden mallet with elongated head, traditionally used to pound rice "
"or millet. It can also smash heads in a pinch."
msgstr "一把头部细长的大木槌，传统上用于捣米或小米。紧急时也能用来砸碎脑袋。"

#: .\youkai_snippets.json
msgid ""
"GHOST SIGHTINGS: TRUTH OR FICTION? Some people have seen recently what they "
"describe as \"paranormal activities\" such as strange lights seen near "
"swamps or rivers, and more. \"I seen one of them, it was the size of a "
"bobcat and pulled my poor dog under the water!\", said one of the supposed "
"witnesses."
msgstr ""
"幽灵目击事件：真相还是虚构？最近有些人看到了他们描述的“超自然活动”，例如在沼泽或河流附近看到奇怪的光等等。“我见过其中一个，它和短尾猫一样大，把我可怜的狗拖到了水下！”一位所谓的目击者说道。"

#: .\youkai_snippets.json
msgid ""
"LITTLE RED MEN: Among many recent strange sightings, there have been already"
" more than 52 people claiming to have seen bizarrely dressed men vandalizing"
" churches and synagogues. Supposedly these hooligans are wearing robes and "
"are painted all red, head to toe. Government sources have since suspected "
"\"Chinese communist agitators\"."
msgstr ""
"小红人：在众多最近的奇怪目击事件中，已有超过52人声称看到穿着奇装异服的男子破坏教堂和犹太教堂。据称这些流氓穿着长袍，从头到脚涂成红色。政府消息来源随后怀疑是“中国共产主义煽动者”。"

#: .\youkai_snippets.json
msgid ""
"AN UNSUSPECTED TRAGEDY: Recently a young girl has been found dead near the "
"road to a remote village. Her body was covered wholly in signs of animal "
"claws, probably ones of a domesticated cat but the cause of death has not "
"been yet uncovered by the police."
msgstr "一场意想不到的悲剧：最近在通往一个偏远村庄的道路附近发现了一名年轻女孩的尸体。她的全身布满了动物爪痕，可能是家猫的，但死因尚未被警方查明。"

#: .\youkai_snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Among all of the demons I have seen I noticed many rivalries. I seen them "
"tear each other apart because of them instead of slaughtering me, thank God."
" The ones from our world really hate those new intruders but are not willing"
" to put old grudges away...\""
msgstr ""
"“在我见过的所有恶魔中，我注意到许多敌对关系。我看到它们因为这些敌对关系而互相撕碎，而不是屠杀我，感谢上帝。来自我们世界的那些真的憎恨那些新入侵者，但又不愿放下旧怨……”"

#: .\youkai_snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"The so called capital \"C\" \"CULT\", is just a bunch of heretics "
"following those spirits alien to us. WE need to embrace OUR inner demons. "
"REJOICE BROTHERS, FOR NEW DAWN IS COMING!\""
msgstr ""
"\"所谓的大写'C'的'邪教'，不过是一群追随那些与我们格格不入的异界灵体的异端罢了。我们应当拥抱内心的恶魔。欢庆吧，兄弟们，因为新的黎明即将来临！\""

#: .\youkai_snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"WE SHOULDN'T HAVE ANGERED THE SPIRITS. WE SHOULDN'T HAVE CUTTED THOSE TREES. WE SHOULDN'T HAVE MINED THOSE MOUNTAINS. GOD LEFT US AND NOW GODS WILL DEVOUR US...\" \n"
" Rest of the text is unintelligible and covered in dried up blood."
msgstr ""
"\"我们不该激怒那些灵体。我们不该砍伐那些树木。我们不该挖掘那些山脉。神已离我们而去，如今众神将吞噬我们……\"\n"
"余下的文字难以辨认，且覆盖着干涸的血迹。"

#: .\youkai_snippets.json
msgid ""
"RISING SUN: Recently an eccentric billionaire, known only by his online "
"trading pseudonym \"Stephen\", started building a new chain of hotels in our"
" state, one that claims to combine modern technology and traditional "
"Japanese architecture to pose a unique experience for its guests."
msgstr ""
"旭日酒店：最近，一位仅以其在线交易化名\"斯蒂芬\"为人所知的古怪亿万富翁，开始在我们州建造一系列新酒店，声称将现代科技与传统日式建筑相结合，为客人提供独特的体验。"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"Leave what's dearest to you for me and I just might leave you alone.\""
msgstr "\"把你最珍贵的东西留给我，我说不定就会放过你。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"Give me that trinket!\""
msgstr "\"把那小玩意儿给我！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"I didn't expect less.\""
msgstr "\"我早就料到了。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"We now rule in this world mortal, remember that.\""
msgstr "\"如今是我们统治这个世界，凡人，记住这一点。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"Just don't call us mere \"demons\" mortal, we are far greater than that.\""
msgstr "\"别把我们叫做区区'恶魔'，凡人，我们远比那更伟大。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"One more yon and I will buy me some sake at Boss's place.\""
msgstr "\"再干一票，我就能去老板那儿买点清酒了。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"Our Boss would love to have another head mounted in his castle.\""
msgstr "\"我们老板会很高兴在他的城堡里再挂上一颗头颅。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"Wait for Boss to hear about this!\""
msgstr "\"等着让老板知道这事吧！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "a loud croak!"
msgstr "一声响亮的呱叫！"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "a thunderclap-like battlecry!"
msgstr "一声雷鸣般的战吼！"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"I am a god!  How could you kill a god?\""
msgstr "\"我是神！你怎么可能杀死一位神？\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"This is pathetic!\""
msgstr "\"这太可悲了！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"You had it coming.\""
msgstr "\"你这是自找的。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"Too bad.  I will have to clean my naginata after this!\""
msgstr "\"真可惜。之后我得好好擦擦我的薙刀了！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"How much do people need to tell you to leave things how they are?\""
msgstr "\"人们得说多少遍你才肯让事物保持原样？\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"A mortal is most useful when it is away.\""
msgstr "\"凡人最有用的时刻，就是他们不在的时候。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "a quiet whistle"
msgstr "一声轻柔的口哨"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"All I need is to stay alone.\""
msgstr "\"我只需要独自待着。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Others of my race would rob your corpse naked but I will be more gentle "
"with it.\""
msgstr "\"我族中的其他家伙会把你的尸体扒个精光，但我会更温柔些。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Your kind is so adaptive which always impressed me.  Too bad your time on "
"Earth is over.\""
msgstr "\"你们这类生物适应性如此之强，总是令我印象深刻。可惜你们在地球上的时日到头了。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"What's this?  A mortal who is putting up a fight? That's cute!\""
msgstr "\"这是什么？一个敢于反抗的凡人？真可爱！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"My fur!  Now it's all icky.\""
msgstr "\"我的毛！现在全弄脏了。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"I hope this human has some lamp oil, haven't tasted it in a while...\""
msgstr "\"希望这个人类身上有点灯油，好久没尝过了……\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"My claws are much sharper than those of a lesser feline!\""
msgstr "\"我的爪子可比那些低等猫科动物锋利多了！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Hmmm, my fish bone comb makes my fur stink a bit. Should I get a human "
"bone one instead?\""
msgstr "\"嗯，我的鱼骨梳让我的毛有点臭。是不是该换个人骨梳子？\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "a quiet meow."
msgstr "一声轻柔的喵叫。"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "a loud meow!"
msgstr "一声响亮的喵叫！"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"All of your kind that survived seem to have at least one mental defect.  "
"Are you another case of a hoader?\""
msgstr "\"你们这些幸存下来的同类，似乎至少都带点精神缺陷。你也是那种囤积癖患者吗？\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"For how much yon does a fish sell this day anyway?\""
msgstr "\"话说今儿个鱼卖多少钱来着？\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "a bizarre croak!"
msgstr "一声怪异的呱呱叫！"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"Cucumber, cucumber, delicious cucumber... ~\"."
msgstr "\"黄瓜，黄瓜，美味的黄瓜……~\"。"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"There is one negative aspect to this apocalypse - no more mortal "
"offsprings to eat.\""
msgstr "\"这场末日浩劫有个坏处——再也吃不到凡人的子嗣了。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Knowing that all humans left are potential youkai hunters always make me "
"jumpy.\""
msgstr "\"一想到剩下的人类都可能是妖怪猎人，我就总是提心吊胆的。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"You humans just work all day on the shore, let me take you where it's "
"wetter and better!\""
msgstr "\"你们人类整天在岸边忙活，让我带你去更湿润、更美妙的地方吧！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Humans are icky when they move, but nowadays they tend to carry a lot of "
"useful parts.\""
msgstr "\"人类动起来时黏糊糊的，不过如今他们身上常带着不少有用的零件。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"HEY!  You have tools, right?!  I mean, what fools don't walk with their "
"tools?\""
msgstr "\"嘿！你带着工具对吧？！我是说，哪个傻瓜出门会不带工具？\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"Building robots while humans are gone is soooo much fun!\""
msgstr "\"趁着人类消失的时候造机器人，简直太——好玩啦！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"On a scale from 1 to 10 I would give this idiocy a solid 9.\""
msgstr "\"按1到10分来算，我给这种蠢事打9分，妥妥的。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"Gimmie all your stuff mortal!\""
msgstr "\"把你所有的东西都交出来，凡人！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"I am gonna drink some sake after that one.\""
msgstr "\"干完这一票，我得去喝点清酒。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"HAH! Is that all you have?\""
msgstr "\"哈！你就这点本事？\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"I'd love to eat something good at Boss's place.  Hope you deliver!\""
msgstr "\"真想在老大那儿吃点好的。希望你能送货上门！\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "a loud shout!"
msgstr "一声大喊！"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "a loud stomp!"
msgstr "一记重踏！"

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"I smash mortals like you into dust.\""
msgstr "\"我要把你这样的凡人砸成粉末。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid ""
"\"I spot with my little third eye that you will be quite a good catch for "
"the day.\""
msgstr "\"我用我的第三只小眼睛发现，你今天会是个不错的猎物。\""

#: .\youkai_speech.json
msgid "\"It's all over when you mess with an ogre.\""
msgstr "\"惹上鬼族，你就完蛋了。\""
